FW Denver VisitOriginal Message From Whitt Mark Sent Monday October PM To Ringwelski Mark Cc Felling Amy Subject RE Denver Visit I will be out the th but should be in the th Amy Felling should be your contact on the th She is most familiar with our computer systems The Enron North America offices are at th St Suite in Downtown Denver The office is over Square Feet but is currently under construction in order to sublease approximately half of that space We currently have employees I believe that you have copied all of the Enron offices that I know of The only other potential office is EOTT Let me know if you need anything else Original Message From Ringwelski Mark Sent Monday October PM To Whitt Mark Cc DuBose Heidi Jurgens Kristen Bierbach Brian Hurst Lonnie Comstock Steve Beers Chad Cigarroa Gabriella Subject Denver Visit Mark Brian and Steve Further to my conversation two weeks ago with Mark I would like to schedule a visit to Denver As a reminder Business Controls is looking at the security posture of Enron facilities worldwide Currently we are focusing our resources on domestic sites At the moment I am planning for one of our IT specialists to travel from Portland to assist me with reviewing IT backup procedures recovery and continuity issues If I could impose on you to provide some information about the office it would greatly help in our planning In particular could you briefly describe the offices physical location which floor how large how many employees and any other Enron subsidiaries or offices in Denver Additionally would you be our point of contact or can you designate someone Thank you in advance for your attention to this matter Mark C Ringwelski Systems and Architecture Business Controls Enron Corporation Phone Cell FAX
passwordlogon afellin password htownbaby Theresa can you please log on to my computer when you have a second this morning I need to remote into it to get some files Thanks Amy

FW Get your Season Pass Details enclosedOriginal Message From mailto Sent Thursday August AM To NRONCOM Subject Get your Season Pass Details enclosed Hey Amy Dont limit yourself to just one mountain this winter season Keep all of your days exciting and fresh with a pass that lets you ski or ride up to five of Colorados top ski resorts for an unbelievable deal See the pass options below for Vail Keystone Breckenridge Beaver Creek and Arapahoe Basin and choose the one thats best for you Dont wait these deals wont be available for long For season pass pricing and purchase information see below THE COLORADO PASStm Adults Kids ages The Colorado Pass offers unlimited skiing and riding at Keystone Breckenridge and Arapahoe Basin all season long plus days at Vail and Beaver Creek The Colorado Pass is not valid at Vail and Beaver Creek Or purchase the Colorado Pass valid for days at Vail and Beaver Creek for for adults for kids To get this price the day Colorado Pass must be purchased during pass sales BUDDY PASStm Adults Kids ages The Buddy Pass offers unlimited unrestricted skiing and riding at Keystone Breckenridge and Arapahoe Basin all season long Youll also be able to ski Vail and Beaver Creek at a discounted rate INTRODUCING TWO NEW OPTIONS THE FOURPACK at Keystone for a day pass THE FIVEPACK at Keystone Breckenridge and Arapahoe Basin for a day pass Passes are valid for allotted number of days any time during the season except and every Saturday in March Passes cannot be resold Only one lift ticket per day may be used THE COLORADO CARDtm Dont want a pass No problem Sign up for the free Colorado Card and youll get discounts on lift tickets at all five resorts all season long Youll be able to ski or ride for as low as per day TO PURCHASE YOUR WINTER PASS Stop by our booth at SNIAGRAB the Taste of Colorado or the CUCSU Football game this Labor Day Weekend OR visit one of the locations listed below in person FridaySunday during store hours August September Current Colorado Pass and Buddy Pass holders can renew their new pass online at beginning September COLORADO SKI AND GOLF Aurora Arvada Littleton GRAND WEST OUTFITTERS Colorado Springs Denver BOULDER SKI DEALS Boulder REI Colorado Springs Denver Fort Collins Littleton Park Meadows Westminster The Pack and Pack will also be available at Front Range King Soopers locations Passes will also be sold at the following resort locations Saturday and Sunday only from ampm through September Lionshead Season Pass Office in Vail Breckenridge Peak Season Pass Office and the River Run Ticket Office in Keystone FOR MORE INFORMATION CALL PS You are receiving this email because you have subscribed to receive SteepSavers If you would like to change your subscription options or remove yourself from this list please go to the following URL cpemprofileaspemail NRONCOM If the URL is not clickable simply copy the URL and paste it into your browser
